  Removing old version and marking stable.

  22 Jun 2005; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org> hwsetup-1.0-r2.ebuild,
  hwsetup-1.0-r3.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc on request of gustavoz.

